FBIS4-37002 "drnes116_j_94008" FBIS-NES-94-116 Daily Report 15 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Defense Council Meets on Military Situation Defense Council Meets on Military Situation EA1506114594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 0430 GMT 15 Jun 94 EA1506114594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in Arabic 0430 GMT 15 Jun 94 Arabic BFN [Text] The National Defense Council met yesterday evening under the chairmanship of [words indistinct] the deputy prime minister. ADEN NEWS AGENCY has learned that the council discussed the military situation at the various fronts and the military activity of the people's resistance movement to confront the forces of injustice and aggression. The Council also discussed the results of the visit of the UN secretary general's envoy, His Excellency Lakhdar Brahimi [words indistinct]. The Council also [word indistinct] the temporary measures adopted to overcome the consequences of the military aggression launched by the [passage indistinct].
